{"id":"cli/help","title":"ng help","contents":"\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/help.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/help.json\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/help\", \"name\": \"help\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-help\">ng help<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/help#ng-help\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">列出可用的命令，及其短描述。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Lists available commands and their short descriptionEns.</p>\n\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">help</span> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------說明----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/help-long.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/help-long.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        說明\n    </h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">要獲得關於單個命令的幫助，請在命令中使用 <code>--help</code> 或 <code>-h</code> 選項。</p><p translation-result=\"on\"> 比如，</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"> For help with individual commands, use the <code>--help</code> or <code>-h</code> option with the command.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"> For example,</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"sh\">\nng help serve\n</code-example>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">選項</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th width=\"15%\">選項</th>\n      <th width=\"40%\">說明</th>\n      <th>Value Type</th>\n      <th>Default Value</th>\n      </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">在控制檯顯示關於本命令的幫助資訊。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n\n        \n      </td>\n      <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true|false|json|JSON</code></td>\n      <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/help#ng-help\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/help-long.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/help.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/help-long.md\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/help.json\n-->"}